title: Rigmar Radio Karaoke Collection 54100
description:
400 More classic Karaoke Songs in CDG+MP3 format.  

New in last years 2015 collection I have been adding Karaoke Label info to the title string to give multiple Label choice on some of the more popular songs and re ripping from the original CD and Laser Discs at a higher Audio Sample rate.  

This is work in progress and should be finished by this time next year, when of course you should have the 2016 collection.

We have reached the letter V.  Enjoy

Rigmar Radio - Rockin' the Free World since 1967
